---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Testimonials & Parent Feedback | Jyoti Girls PG"
  description="Hear what parents and students say about Jyoti Girls PG near Osmanpura, from safety to study support."
>

  <section style="padding: 60px 0 40px; background: var(--color-bg-base);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Girls PG near Osmanpura</span>
      <h1 class="section-heading">Testimonials &amp; Parent Feedback</h1>
      <p class="section-lead">Families choose Jyoti Girls PG for its trustworthy environment, transparent communication, and sustained academic guidance.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Parent Stories</h2>
      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="card testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial-quote">"We shifted to Jyoti Girls PG after comparing four hostels around Osmanpura. The warden's daily updates and spotless premises assure us that our daughter is safe."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">Mrs. Kadam</div>
          <div class="testimonial-role">Parent of NEET aspirant</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial-quote">"The team handled my daughter's dietary allergies with care. Even during exam season, meals were prepared exactly as instructed."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">Mr. Shaikh</div>
          <div class="testimonial-role">Parent of FYMBBS student</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial-quote">"Late evening curfew calls and entry logs are shared with us. It is rare to find such accountability in a PG."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">Mrs. Patil</div>
          <div class="testimonial-role">Parent of Class 12 student</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial-quote">"As a parent, the homely environment put our minds at ease. The staff keeps us updated every week about routines and progress."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">Mrs. Deshpande</div>
          <div class="testimonial-role">Parent</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-subtle);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Student Experiences</h2>
      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="card testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial-quote">"I revised comfortably because the study hall stays open with quiet supervision. The proximity to Osmanpura institutes saves nearly an hour daily."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">Riya S.</div>
          <div class="testimonial-role">NEET dropper</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial-quote">"Laundry and housekeeping are taken care of, so I can focus on college projects. Weekend yoga sessions are a bonus."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">Aastha L.</div>
          <div class="testimonial-role">B.Tech student</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial-quote">"The mess food tastes close to home. When I fell ill, the caretaker accompanied me to the doctor within minutes."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">Trisha M.</div>
          <div class="testimonial-role">XI Science student</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial-quote">"The study lounge and high-speed Wi-Fi make group projects simple. It genuinely feels like a supportive, secure community."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">Ritika Patil</div>
          <div class="testimonial-role">Engineering Student</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Support from Educators</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:20px;max-width:600px;margin-bottom:40px;">
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Coaching mentors compliment the disciplined study routine maintained by the warden.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">College faculty often refer newcomers because of consistent attendance and punctuality of PG residents.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Visiting counsellors note the stress-free ambience and regular parental communication.</li>
      </ul>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <button class="btn-primary" data-modal="availability">Request reference list</button>
        <a href="https://wa.me/919922333305?text=Hello%20Jyoti%20Girls%20PG%2C%20please%20share%20resident%20references." class="btn-whatsapp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Message now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
